{"words":[{"word":"beast","count":5},{"word":"bei","count":5},{"word":"shi","count":5},{"word":"jingle","count":4},{"word":"yes","count":3},{"word":"wanted","count":3},{"word":"promise","count":3},{"word":"sorry","count":3},{"word":"thought","count":2},{"word":"happy","count":2},{"word":"knew","count":2},{"word":"proud","count":2},{"word":"show","count":2},{"word":"find","count":2},{"word":"fear","count":2},{"word":"something","count":2},{"word":"actually","count":2},{"word":"made","count":2},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"kill","count":1},{"word":"sister","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"rumors","count":1},{"word":"exile","count":1},{"word":"group","count":1},{"word":"called","count":1},{"word":"savages","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"prove","count":1},{"word":"courage","count":1},{"word":"timid","count":1},{"word":"brother","count":1},{"word":"end","count":1},{"word":"achieve","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"failed","count":1},{"word":"beat","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"guys","count":1},{"word":"cower","count":1},{"word":"incompetent","count":1},{"word":"coward","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"r-really","count":1},{"word":"okay","count":1},{"word":"um","count":1},{"word":"least","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"so-called","count":1},{"word":"bluff","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"imagination","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"tacet","count":1},{"word":"discords","count":1},{"word":"playername","count":1},{"word":"lingyang","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"caused","count":1},{"word":"eh","count":1},{"word":"tomorrow","count":1},{"word":"request","count":1},{"word":"investigate","count":1},{"word":"guess","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"necessary","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"amazing","count":1},{"word":"joined","count":1},{"word":"association","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"chasing","count":1},{"word":"dreams","count":1},{"word":"erm","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"forgive","count":1},{"word":"treat","count":1},{"word":"sincere","count":1},{"word":"apology","count":1},{"word":"awesome","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Yeah... I thought I could kill the Jingle Beast, and make my sister happy again...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"And I heard rumors about an Exile group called \"The Savages.\" Said they knew how to talk to that beast...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"So I thought...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Yes... I wanted to prove my courage. Wanted to make her proud of me.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"I just wanted to show her... If her timid brother could do it, so can she!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"But in the end, I couldn't achieve anything...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Yes, you're right...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"I failed. Couldn't find the Jingle Beast, couldn't beat the bad guys. I only knew how to cower in fear... that's all I could do.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"I'm just an incompetent coward. I've always been!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"R-really...?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Okay, yes, I promise you... But, um, at least I did find something this time!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"We now know the so-called Jingle Beast is just a bluff!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"So, Bei Shi, you don't need to fear it anymore!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Perhaps it was just your imagination? Or maybe it was some Tacet Discords?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"{PlayerName}, Lingyang, we'll be going home now. Sorry for the trouble I caused.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Eh? Tomorrow?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"No, no, I didn't...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Sorry. Actually, I made that request to further investigate the Jingle Beast...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"But now, I guess that's no longer necessary.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"I see. We'll come watch the show!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Bei Shi, that's amazing!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"When you joined the Association, I was actually so proud... I'm happy you get to keep chasing your dreams...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"And, erm, please forgive me...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"I promise, I promise. Let me treat you to something as my sincere apology.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Awesome! Bei Shi, let's go!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Bei Shi...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Bei Shi, I'm so sorry I made you worry...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031}]}